text: Barbara Frackiewicz is a former Polish long track speed skater, who was active in the 1960s. Frackiewicz represented her nation at the World Allround Speed Skating Championships for Women in 1962, finishing 29th overall. She also competed at other international competitions. At the 1962 Polish Allround Championships she finished 5th.
